<h3 class="has-text-weight-light">How We Work</h3>
<p>Music Management & Development at Music Gateway works a little differently in that our managers do not take a percentage of your rights, instead working on a consultation basis to offer you expert advice, so you remain in control every step of the way. Supported by a successful in-house <a href="/music-promotion"> music promotion</a> team, we act as a springboard from where you are now to where you want to be next.</p>
